2) If companies are hard up for finding cheaper ways of getting the job done now, what will happen the next time the Government wants to raise the Minimum wage to match inflation?  It's only going to further stress the desire to send work over seas to more <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>unregulated</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> working countries.<br>
